# SuperOps API Collection

A sanitized Postman collection containing sample API requests and workflows built around the SuperOps platform.

This repository showcases practical API usage across IT operations, service management, and customer support workflows.

## Included Modules

- Asset Management APIs
- Ticket Management APIs
- Client / Account APIs
- Requester / Contact APIs
- Contract APIs
- IT Documentation APIs
- GraphQL Queries
- Workflow Automation Use Cases

## Use Cases

- Retrieve asset details and activity logs
- Create and manage tickets
- Fetch ticket conversations and notes
- Manage client and requester information
- Access contracts and documentation records
- Build custom automations using APIs

